No, let go of me!
Contrary to the name, Yumyum is not
actually at all yummy!

rows.label: qst200712_msg0002

Attacked by Ignas?
Is par for course, mo.

He's kind of a friend by now, isn't he?
We should probably help!

rows.label: qst200712_msg0005

Let's save Yumyum, then we'll talk
mushroom!

rows.label: qst200712_msg0006
rows.name:
It might actually taste better
after some light exercise!
